  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为FinTech账本服务设计一个清晰的架构图。核心模块是LedgerService控制器，它要处理所有的交易请求入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controllers",
        "FinTech_LedgerService"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，LedgerService作为控制器层。那业务逻辑层怎么规划？是直接调用数据访问，还是需要中间层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controllers",
        "Services"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "必须加Services层，叫TransactionQueue。交易请求先进队列，异步处理，不能阻塞控制器。Services层承上启下。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Services",
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，Controllers使用Services。数据持久化部分呢？PaymentGateway作为仓储层？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controllers",
        "Services",
        "Repositories",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Repositories层用PaymentGateway对接第三方支付渠道。还有DomainModels层，核心领域模型是AuthVault，存用户凭证和权限状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Repositories",
        "DomainModels",
        "FinTech_PaymentGateway",
        "FinTech_AuthVault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下关系：Services使用Repositories，Repositories持久化到DomainModels？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Services",
        "Repositories",
        "DomainModels"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。另外需要DTOs层做数据传输，FraudDetection专门做风控检查结果的数据封装，控制器返回给前端用。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DTOs",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "Controllers"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加，Controllers返回DTOs。设计模式这块需要体现吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Controllers",
        "DTOs",
        "Patterns"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，Patterns层也放FraudDetection，但这里是策略模式的具体实现，Services层调用它来做风控规则引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patterns",
        "FinTech_FraudDetection",
        "Services"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Services使用Patterns。安全模块怎么设计？AuthVault已经在DomainModels里了。",
